{{one source|date=February 2017}} {{Infobox football biography | name = Karol Tomczyk | fullname = Karol Tomczyk | birth_date = 5 September 1989 | birth_place = [[Czestochowa]], [[Poland]] | height = 187cm | position = [[defender (association football)|center-back]] | currentclub = | clubnumber = | years1 = –2012 | clubs1 = [[Polonia Bytom]] | caps1 = 3 | goals1 = 0 | years2 = 2013–2014 | clubs2 = [[Widzew Lodz]] | caps2 = 1 | goals2 = 0 | years3 = 2014– | clubs3 = [https://pl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skra_Cz%C4%99stochowa Skra Częstochowa] }}
'''Karol Tomczyk''' is a [[Poles|Polish]] footballer who last played for [[Widzew Lodz]].<ref>http://sport.wp.pl/kat,53716,title,Kowalski-i-Tomczyk-na-wylocie-z-Widzewa,wid,16378779,wiadomosc.html</ref>
Altogether, the 187&nbsp;cm-tall defender has made two cup appearances for past side [[Polonia Bytom]]. Spending a winter looking for clubs to join, he joined [[Widzew Lodz]] in the transfer window, playing one game. [[Widzew Lodz]] proceeded to terminate his contract since extended game time was improbable, forcing him to go to [https://pl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skra_Cz%C4%99stochowa Skra Częstochowa].<ref>http://www.widzewtomy.net/aktualnosci/karol-tomczyk-pilkarzem-skry-czestochowa/</ref>
