'''Stade de Kadiogo''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Kadiogo]], [[Burkina Faso]].  It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Rail Club du Kadiogo]].  The stadium holds 8,000 people.

