{{Coord|32.215438|-98.220617|display=title}} '''Wisdom Gymnasium''' is a 3,000 seat multi-purpose arena in [[Stephenville, Texas|Stephenville]], [[Texas]]. It was built in 1970.<ref>http://tarletonsports.com/sports/2009/8/24/MBB_0824092714.aspx?id=72</ref> It is the home of the [[Tarleton State University]] Texans basketball teams and volleyball team. Wisdom Gymnasium is named for long-time Tarleton athletics director and coach W.J. Wisdom.
